snippet.textDisplay:
WOW!!! Amazing, I just have been reunited with the one and only love of my life after almost exactly one year, after breaking up in December 27, 2018 and being reunited on December 7 of this year and she knows how deeply I love her and I know she does as well, but I have been trying to find the perfect words and or song and as I was just about to go to bed minutes ago, a notification came up on my phone to listen to this song!!

Now I know why, convinced God just did that for me to send her the link to this song!!

Thank you Blake and Gwen, you two are so in love and that is so easy to see.... your voices and your lyrics confirm that even more!

This will now be the love of my life and my song for the rest of our lives together... lots of love
